comments: I am not sure if I noticed the correct pattern with the alien words but all the words ended with 'coh' and the pronunciation kind of sounded the same with the 'u' after the first letter and the 'i' after the second. It was a bit difficult for me to memorize the words at first (as I was also trying to memorize the shapes), I had to say the words out loud for me actually remember them and the spelling kind of messed with me at first but I got a hang of it as I kept on training. There could have a pattern with the colors also but it was very difficult to pay attention to that as already my focus on the shape and the names.
